<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>Retrieve log shipping tokens</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"post"} path={"/v1/log-shipping/tokens/search"}></MethodEndpoint>



Returns the relevant shipping tokens, filtered, sorted and paginated as per the request. 
Please ensure to change the region in the URL to match your account's region.
